reviewtxt:
This is your typical little Italy cafe. Pastries were fine ! Nothing exceeding my Italian dessert cravings... it's very pretty inside . I could sit there and read a book and munch on Napoleons all day (but I won't). Everyone at my table was happy with what they got. Well air conditioned.. out door seating... attentive staff. 

Xoxo
